OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnion calls for heat limit 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flaw in workplaces          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A union has called for a legal limit on
OL,6, how hot it can be in a workplace ahead 
OL,7, of a red warning for extreme heat.     
OL,9,FThe GMB union said workers should not  
OL,10,Fhave to contend with temperatures any  
OL,11,Fhigher than 25C, as forecasters predict
OL,12,Fa record high of 41C (106F) in England.
OL,14,FThe Met Office's highest warning covers
OL,15,Fan area including London, Manchester   
OL,16,Fand York on Monday and Tuesday.        
OL,18,FThere is currently no law in the UK or 
OL,19,FIreland which states any given         
OL,20,Ftemperature is too hot or cold to work.
